  "type": "mcq",
  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">Oil and gas production in a certain area dropped from 4&nbsp;million&nbsp;barrels in 2000 to 1.9&nbsp;million&nbsp;barrels in 2013. Assuming that the oil and gas production decreased at a constant rate, which of the following linear functions <span class=\"italic\">f</span> best models the production, in millions of barrels, <span class=\"italic\">t</span> years after the year 2000?</p>\n",
  "answerOptions": [
