      "content": "<p><span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"f of t equals, the fraction 21 over 130, end fraction, t plus 4\"></span></span></p>\n"
